//! Project: baton (cli)
//! AC description: `baton send <sid> <prompt>` constructs a valid AGORABUS_RPC envelope with method=baton.send, params.prompt set, and an `id` matching ^rpc-baton-[a-z0-9]+$.
//! Test predicate: tests/acceptance_ac3.rs
